# Trapeza adapter rules

All Circle/Arc SDK calls stay in `packages/adapter-arc/` or `packages/adapter-gateway/`.
Never import chain SDKs from `@trapeza/core`.

## Locked constants

Check existing values before adding new ones:

- `packages/adapter-gateway/src/constants.ts` — USDC, Gateway Wallet, Arc testnet chain
- `packages/adapter-arc/src/constants.ts` — ERC-8004 registry addresses, Arc testnet

## Arc USDC gotcha

On Arc testnet, USDC is the native gas token. The ERC-20 at `0x3600000000000000000000000000000000000000`
uses **6 decimals**; the native gas view uses **18 decimals**. They reflect the same balance.
A single faucet drop funds both gas and x402 payments.

